%N A395476 Expansion of e.g.f. x^3*(1 + x + x^2/2)*exp(x).
%C A395476 Number of words of length n defined on {a, b, c, d, e} that contain one a, one b, one c, at most two d's, and any number of e's.
%F A395476 a(n) = n*(n-1)*(n-2)*(n^2-5*n+8)/2.
%F A395476 a(n) = 6*binomial(n,3)*Sum_{k=0..2} binomial(n-3,k).
